# Contributing

## How to contribute

1. Fork the repo
2. Edit or add markdown files in the relevant section folder
3. Submit a pull request

## Adding Discord questions

Paste unanswered or commonly repeated Discord questions into a `questions.md` file inside the relevant section folder. Anyone with AI access can use these as input to draft or improve guide content.

## File structure

Each section folder contains:
- `README.md` — the main guide content for that progression range
- `questions.md` — Discord questions for that range (input for improvement)

## Discord blocks

Each `README.md` ends with a `## Discord` section — the exact text to paste as a Discord pin, kept under 2,000 characters.

## Accuracy

Claims should be verifiable against the [Synergism source code](https://github.com/pseudo-corp/SynergismOfficial). If you're unsure, note it with a `> ⚠ unverified` blockquote.
